<node TEXT="For whale individual recognition we elaborated another system to compare the in-dividuals by applying BoW model, during which Harris-Laplace detector and dense SIFT for creating low-level features. After that we calculated the GMM based Fisher vectors and then we compared them to each other with RBF kernel function, but first-ly we tried several distance measurements. In addition to this we tried background segmentation as preprocessing. " ID="ID_1459851094" CREATED="1501336855106" MODIFIED="1501336855106" LINK="project://15D6452E29D9SKCYL8S32EEF1MB7Z0BV75KJ/literature_repository/papers/Counting%20Measurement%20Identification%20Tracking/2016%20Object%20detection,%20classification,%20tracking%20and%20individual%20recognition%20for%20sea%20images%20and%20videos.pdf">
